    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/859238fa78624f2cc3184c69b537d465.avif?t=1769086134\" width=1560 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the grim depths of the underworld - the Pit, fight with its ferocious inhabitants, and determine your own fate in this classic first-person aRPG with immersive elements, created for fans of the genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/0294258cc3f3e747993bacb04a48751b.poster.avif?t=1769086134\" width=798 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/0294258cc3f3e747993bacb04a48751b.webm?t=1769086134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/044b278f9094c6ae4d4a21f3a62dd7eb.avif?t=1769086134\" width=1560 height=110 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the open underground world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape the ruins of the Old Prison, reach the main underground city of Hometown, break through the lair of the Wererats, infiltrate the abandoned laboratory of the Mechans, and delve into other meticulously crafted locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight formidable enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in battles with dangerous foes that inhabit the Pit. Use your combat skills and a wide arsenal to gain the upper hand and survive in this ruthless, danger-filled place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve riddles and uncover hidden elements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a variety of puzzles, unearth hidden secrets, and collect valuable items that unlock new opportunities and help you progress deeper into the abandoned corners of the underground world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/7eb16269e887131cf320c6c09260b99a.avif?t=1769086134\" width=1560 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/cbd7b2049acba0782671e8d9731758c8.poster.avif?t=1769086134\" width=798 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/cbd7b2049acba0782671e8d9731758c8.webm?t=1769086134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Immersive Combat System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into dynamic and thrilling battles, controlling every strike and movement. Use a variety of weapons and find your own style to masterfully defeat enemies and feel like a true fighter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/e9c4c0c402243182470c40a43a637153.poster.avif?t=1769086134\" width=798 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176780/extras/e9c4c0c402243182470c40a43a637153.webm?t=1769086134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deep Atmospheric Immersion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the living, dark world of the Pit, interact with the environment, and make difficult decisions that will affect both you and the fate of the underground world, forever doomed to never see the sun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Well-crafted Lore</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the grim history of this place. Here, every note, symbol, and forgotten corner comes together to form a single, living, breathing universe. Delve into its mysteries and Step into the Dark, where ancient secrets lie waiting to be uncovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
